       AC000-READ              SECTION.

       READ-CONTROL.
             READ NETWORK.
           IF WS-STATUS = "00"
               GO TO READ-CONTROL-EXIT.
           IF WS-STAT1 = "2" OR "3" OR "4"
               MOVE 2            TO WS-F-ERROR
               PERFORM READ-ERROR.
           IF RECORD-LOCKED
               PERFORM LOCKED-RECORD
               GO TO READ-CONTROL.
             MOVE 2              TO WS-F-ERROR.
             PERFORM READ-ERROR.
             GO TO READ-CONTROL-EXIT.

       READ-CONTROL-LOCK.
             READ NETWORK WITH KEPT LOCK.
           IF WS-STATUS = "00"
               GO TO READ-CONTROL-EXIT.
           IF WS-STAT1 = "2" OR "3" OR "4"
               MOVE 2            TO WS-F-ERROR
               PERFORM READ-ERROR.
           IF RECORD-LOCKED
               PERFORM LOCKED-RECORD
               GO TO READ-CONTROL-LOCK.
           IF TOO-MANY-LOCKS
               UNLOCK NETWORK
               GO TO READ-CONTROL-LOCK.
             MOVE 2              TO WS-F-ERROR.
             PERFORM READ-ERROR.

