             PERFORM READ-ERROR.

       READ-DEPART-EXIT.
             EXIT.

       READ-PARAM.
             READ PARAM.
           IF WS-STATUS = "00"
               GO TO READ-PARAM-EXIT.
           IF WS-STAT1 = "2" OR "3" OR "4"
               MOVE 15           TO WS-F-ERROR
               PERFORM READ-ERROR.
           IF RECORD-LOCKED
               PERFORM LOCKED-RECORD
               GO TO READ-PARAM.
             MOVE 15             TO WS-F-ERROR.
             PERFORM READ-ERROR.

       READ-PARAM-LOCK.
           READ PARAM            WITH KEPT LOCK.
           IF WS-STATUS = "00"
               GO TO READ-PARAM-EXIT.
           IF WS-STAT1 = "2" OR "3" OR "4"
               MOVE 15           TO WS-F-ERROR
               PERFORM READ-ERROR.
           IF RECORD-LOCKED
               IF WS-PARKEY = "4"
                   PERFORM LOCK-USERS-REC THRU LOCK-REC-EXIT
                   GO TO READ-PARAM-LOCK
               ELSE
                   PERFORM LOCKED-RECORD
                   GO TO READ-PARAM-LOCK.
           IF TOO-MANY-LOCKS
               UNLOCK PARAM
               GO TO READ-PARAM-LOCK.
             MOVE 15             TO WS-F-ERROR.
             PERFORM READ-ERROR.

       READ-PARAM-EXIT.
             EXIT.
      *
      *     ***  *****  ***   ***  *   *     ***** ***** *     *****
      *    *   *   *   *   * *   * *  *      *       *   *     *
