      *        *   *   *   * *     * *       *       *   *     *
      *    *   *   *   *   * *   * *  *      *       *   *     *
      *     ***    *    ***   ***  *   *     *     ***** ***** *****
      *
       READ-STOCK.
             READ STOCK
               KEY IS STK-CODE.
           IF WS-STATUS = "00"
               MOVE ZERO         TO WS-F-ERROR
               GO TO READ-STOCK-EXIT.
           IF WS-STATUS = "23"
               MOVE 22           TO WS-F-ERROR
               GO TO READ-STOCK-EXIT.
           IF WS-STAT1 = "2" OR "3" OR "4"
               MOVE 22           TO WS-F-ERROR
               PERFORM READ-ERROR.
           IF RECORD-LOCKED
               PERFORM LOCKED-RECORD
               GO TO READ-STOCK.
             GO TO READ-STOCK-EXIT.

       READ-STOCK-LOCK.
             READ STOCK WITH KEPT LOCK
               KEY IS STK-CODE.
           IF WS-STATUS = "00"
               MOVE ZERO         TO WS-F-ERROR
               GO TO READ-STOCK-EXIT.
           IF WS-STATUS = "23"
               MOVE 22           TO WS-F-ERROR
               GO TO READ-STOCK-EXIT.
           IF WS-STAT1 = "2" OR "3" OR "4"
               MOVE 22           TO WS-F-ERROR
               PERFORM READ-ERROR.
           IF RECORD-LOCKED
               PERFORM LOCKED-RECORD
               GO TO READ-STOCK-LOCK.
           IF TOO-MANY-LOCKS
               UNLOCK STOCK
               GO TO READ-STOCK-LOCK.
             GO TO READ-STOCK-EXIT.

       READ-STOCK-NEXT.
             READ STOCK NEXT.
           IF WS-STATUS = "00"
               MOVE ZERO         TO WS-F-ERROR
               GO TO READ-STOCK-EXIT.
           IF (WS-STATUS = "23") OR
              (WS-STAT1 = "1")
               MOVE 22           TO WS-F-ERROR
               GO TO READ-STOCK-EXIT.
           IF WS-STAT1 = "2" OR "3" OR "4"
               MOVE 22           TO WS-F-ERROR
               PERFORM READ-ERROR.
           IF RECORD-LOCKED
               PERFORM LOCKED-RECORD
               GO TO READ-STOCK-NEXT.
             GO TO READ-STOCK-EXIT.

       READ-STOCK-NEXT-LOCK.
             READ STOCK NEXT WITH KEPT LOCK.
           IF WS-STATUS = "00"
               MOVE ZERO         TO WS-F-ERROR
               GO TO READ-STOCK-EXIT.
           IF (WS-STATUS = "23") OR
              (WS-STAT1 = "1")
               MOVE 22           TO WS-F-ERROR
               GO TO READ-STOCK-EXIT.
           IF WS-STAT1 = "2" OR "3" OR "4"
               MOVE 22           TO WS-F-ERROR
               PERFORM READ-ERROR.
           IF RECORD-LOCKED
               PERFORM LOCKED-RECORD
               GO TO READ-STOCK-NEXT-LOCK.
           IF TOO-MANY-LOCKS
               UNLOCK STOCK
               GO TO READ-STOCK-NEXT-LOCK.
             GO TO READ-STOCK-EXIT.

       START-AT-STOCK-CODE.
             START STOCK
               KEY >= STK-CODE.
           IF WS-STATUS = "00"
               MOVE ZERO         TO WS-F-ERROR
               GO TO READ-STOCK-EXIT.
           IF WS-STATUS = "23"
               MOVE 22           TO WS-F-ERROR
               GO TO READ-STOCK-EXIT.
           IF WS-STAT1 = "2" OR "3" OR "4"
               MOVE 22           TO WS-F-ERROR
               PERFORM READ-ERROR.
             GO TO READ-STOCK-EXIT.

       START-AT-ALT-CODE.
             START STOCK
               KEY >= STK-ACODE.
           IF WS-STATUS = "00"
               MOVE ZERO         TO WS-F-ERROR
               GO TO READ-STOCK-EXIT.
           IF WS-STATUS = "23"
               MOVE 22           TO WS-F-ERROR
               GO TO READ-STOCK-EXIT.
           IF WS-STAT1 = "2" OR "3" OR "4"
               MOVE 22           TO WS-F-ERROR
               PERFORM READ-ERROR.
             GO TO READ-STOCK-EXIT.

       START-AT-STOCK-BIN.
             START STOCK
               KEY >= STK-BSEQ.
           IF WS-STATUS = "00"
               MOVE ZERO         TO WS-F-ERROR
               GO TO READ-STOCK-EXIT.
           IF WS-STATUS = "23"
               MOVE 22           TO WS-F-ERROR
               GO TO READ-STOCK-EXIT.
           IF WS-STAT1 = "2" OR "3" OR "4"
               MOVE 22           TO WS-F-ERROR
               PERFORM READ-ERROR.
             GO TO READ-STOCK-EXIT.

       START-AT-STOCK-LEDG.
             START STOCK
               KEY >= STK-LSEQ.
           IF WS-STATUS = "00"
               MOVE ZERO         TO WS-F-ERROR
               GO TO READ-STOCK-EXIT.
           IF WS-STATUS = "23"
               MOVE 22           TO WS-F-ERROR
               GO TO READ-STOCK-EXIT.
           IF WS-STAT1 = "2" OR "3" OR "4"
               MOVE 22           TO WS-F-ERROR
               PERFORM READ-ERROR.
             GO TO READ-STOCK-EXIT.

       START-AT-STOCK-DESC.
             START STOCK
               KEY >= STK-DKEY.
           IF WS-STATUS = "00"
               MOVE ZERO         TO WS-F-ERROR
               GO TO READ-STOCK-EXIT.
           IF WS-STATUS = "23"
               MOVE 22           TO WS-F-ERROR
               GO TO READ-STOCK-EXIT.
           IF WS-STAT1 = "2" OR "3" OR "4"
               MOVE 22           TO WS-F-ERROR
               PERFORM READ-ERROR.
             GO TO READ-STOCK-EXIT.

       START-AT-STOCK-XREF.
             START STOCK
               KEY >= STK-XREF.
           IF WS-STATUS = "00"
               MOVE ZERO         TO WS-F-ERROR
               GO TO READ-STOCK-EXIT.
           IF WS-STATUS = "23"
               MOVE 22           TO WS-F-ERROR
               GO TO READ-STOCK-EXIT.
           IF WS-STAT1 = "2" OR "3" OR "4"
               MOVE 22           TO WS-F-ERROR
               PERFORM READ-ERROR.

       READ-STOCK-EXIT.
             EXIT.
      *
      *     ***  *****  ***   ***  *   *     ***** ****  *****
      *    *   *   *   *   * *   * *  *        *   *   * *
      *    *       *   *   * *     * *         *   *  *  *
      *     ***    *   *   * *     **          *   ***   ***
      *        *   *   *   * *     * *         *   *  *  *
      *    *   *   *   *   * *   * *  *        *   *   * *
      *     ***    *    ***   ***  *   *       *   *   * *
      *
       READ-STKTRF.
             READ STKTRF.
           IF WS-STATUS = "00"
               MOVE ZERO         TO WS-F-ERROR
               GO TO READ-STKTRF-EXIT.
           IF WS-STATUS = "23"
               MOVE 33           TO WS-F-ERROR
               GO TO READ-STKTRF-EXIT.
           IF WS-STAT1 = "2" OR "3" OR "4"
               MOVE 33           TO WS-F-ERROR
               PERFORM READ-ERROR.
           IF RECORD-LOCKED
               PERFORM LOCKED-RECORD
               GO TO READ-STKTRF.

       READ-STKTRF-EXIT.
             EXIT.
      *
      *   R E W R I T E   &    W R I T E   F I L E S   R O U T I N E S
      *
       AD000-WRITE             SECTION.

       REWRITE-CONTROL.
             REWRITE NET-RECORD.
           IF WS-STATUS NOT = "00"
               MOVE 2            TO WS-F-ERROR
               PERFORM WRITE-ERROR.
             GO TO WRITE-CONTROL-EXIT.

       REWRITE-CONTROL-UNLOCK.
             REWRITE NET-RECORD.
           IF WS-STATUS NOT = "00"
               MOVE 2            TO WS-F-ERROR
               PERFORM WRITE-ERROR.
             UNLOCK NETWORK.

       WRITE-CONTROL-EXIT.
             EXIT.

       REWRITE-DEPART.
             REWRITE DPT-RECORD.
           IF WS-STATUS NOT = "00"
               MOVE 7            TO WS-F-ERROR
               PERFORM WRITE-ERROR.
             GO TO WRITE-DEPART-EXIT.

       REWRITE-DEPART-UNLOCK.
             REWRITE DPT-RECORD.
           IF WS-STATUS NOT = "00"
               MOVE 7            TO WS-F-ERROR
               PERFORM WRITE-ERROR.
             UNLOCK DEPART.

       WRITE-DEPART-EXIT.
             EXIT.

       REWRITE-PARAM.
             REWRITE PAR-RECORD1.
           IF WS-STATUS NOT = "00"
               MOVE 15           TO WS-F-ERROR
               PERFORM WRITE-ERROR.
             GO TO WRITE-PARAM-EXIT.

       REWRITE-PARAM-UNLOCK.
             REWRITE PAR-RECORD1.
           IF WS-STATUS NOT = "00"
               MOVE 15           TO WS-F-ERROR
               PERFORM WRITE-ERROR.
             UNLOCK PARAM.

       WRITE-PARAM-EXIT.
             EXIT.
      *
      *     ***  *****  ***   ***  *   *     ***** ***** *     *****
      *    *   *   *   *   * *   * *  *      *       *   *     *
      *    *       *   *   * *     * *       *       *   *     *
      *     ***    *   *   * *     **        ***     *   *     ***
      *        *   *   *   * *     * *       *       *   *     *
      *    *   *   *   *   * *   * *  *      *       *   *     *
      *     ***    *    ***   ***  *   *     *     ***** ***** *****
      *
       REWRITE-STOCK.
             REWRITE STK-RECORD1.
           IF WS-STAT1 NOT = "0"
               MOVE 22           TO WS-F-ERROR
               PERFORM WRITE-ERROR.
             GO TO WRITE-STOCK-EXIT.
      
       REWRITE-STOCK-UNLOCK.
             REWRITE STK-RECORD1.
           IF WS-STAT1 NOT = "0"
               MOVE 22           TO WS-F-ERROR
               PERFORM WRITE-ERROR.
             UNLOCK STOCK.
             GO TO WRITE-STOCK-EXIT.
      
       DELETE-STOCK-REC.
             DELETE STOCK.
           IF WS-STAT1 NOT = "0"
               MOVE 22           TO WS-F-ERROR
               PERFORM WRITE-ERROR.
             UNLOCK STOCK.
             GO TO WRITE-STOCK-EXIT.
      
       WRITE-STOCK.
             WRITE STK-RECORD1.
           IF WS-STAT1 NOT = "0"
               MOVE 22           TO WS-F-ERROR
               PERFORM WRITE-ERROR.
             CLOSE STOCK.
             OPEN I-O STOCK.
      
       WRITE-STOCK-EXIT.
             EXIT.
      *
      *     ***  *****  ***   ***  *   *     ***** ***** *****
      *    *   *   *   *   * *   * *  *        *   *   * *
      *    *       *   *   * *     * *         *   *  *  *
      *     ***    *   *   * *     **          *   ***   ***
      *        *   *   *   * *     * *         *   *  *  *
      *    *   *   *   *   * *   * *  *        *   *   * *
      *     ***    *    ***   ***  *   *       *   *   * *
      *
       REWRITE-STKTRF.
             REWRITE TRF-RECORD1.
           IF WS-STAT1 NOT = "0"
               MOVE 33           TO WS-F-ERROR
               PERFORM WRITE-ERROR.
             GO TO WRITE-STKTRF-EXIT.
      
       WRITE-STKTRF.
             WRITE TRF-RECORD1.
           IF WS-STAT1 NOT = "0"
               MOVE 33           TO WS-F-ERROR
               PERFORM WRITE-ERROR.
             CLOSE STKTRF.
             OPEN I-O STKTRF.
      
       WRITE-STKTRF-EXIT.
             EXIT.

